{"ID":270220, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"220\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs219.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs221.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 220<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Plan of Salvation Before the World Was<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">The great Jehovah contemplated the whole of the events connected with the earth,<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> pertaining\n  to the plan of salvation, before it rolled into existence,<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> or ever &ldquo;the morning stars sang together&rdquo; for\n  joy;<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> the past, the present, and the future were and are, with Him, one eternal &ldquo;now;&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> He knew of\n  the fall of Adam,<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> the iniquities of the antediluvians,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> of the depth of iniquity that would be\n  connected with the human family, their weakness and strength, their power and glory, apostasies,\n  their crimes, their righteousness and iniquity; He comprehended the fall of man,<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> and his\n  redemption; He knew the plan of salvation and pointed it out; He was acquainted with the situation\n  of all nations and with their destiny; He ordered all things according to the council of His own will;\n  He knows the situation of both the living and the dead,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> and has made ample provision for their\n  redemption, according to their several circumstances, and the laws of the kingdom of God,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> whether\n  in this world, or in the world to come.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">False Doctrines in the World<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">The idea that some men form of the justice, judgment, and mercy of God, is too foolish for an\n  intelligent man to think of: for instance, it is common for many of our orthodox preachers to suppose\n  that if a man is not what they call converted, if he dies in that state he must remain eternally in hell\n  without any hope. Infinite years in torment must he spend,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> and never, never, never have an end;\n  and yet this eternal misery<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> is made frequently to rest upon the merest casualty. The breaking of a\n  shoe-string, the tearing of a coat of those officiating, or the peculiar location in which a person lives,\n  may be the means, indirectly of his damnation, or the cause of his not being saved. I will suppose\n  a case which is not extraordinary: Two men, who have been equally wicked, who have neglected\n  religion, are both of them taken sick at the same time; one of them has the good fortune to be visited\n  by a praying man, and he gets converted a few minutes before he dies; the other sends for three\n  different praying men, a tailor, a shoemaker, and a tinman; the tinman has a handle to solder to a\n  can, the tailor has a buttonhole to work on some coat that he needed in a hurry, and the shoemaker\n  has a patch to put on somebody&rsquo;s boot;<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117001\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117001)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117001)\">Abr. 2:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111553\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111553)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111553)\">Mosiah 4:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112016\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112016)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112016)\">Alma 22:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106617\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106617)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106617)\">Job 38:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106341\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106341)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106341)\">Deut. 32:7-8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109136\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109136)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109136)\">Acts 17:26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111106\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111106)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111106)\">2 Ne. 2:24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116721\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116721)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116721)\">Moses 1:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111932\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111932)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111932)\">Alma 13:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115025\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115025)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115025)\">D&amp;C 93:24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116243\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116243)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116243)\">D&amp;C 130:7-8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111544\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111544)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111544)\">Mosiah 3:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112508\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112508)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112508)\">Hel. 14:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116828\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116828)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116828)\">Moses 6:48<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"105994\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 105994)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(105994)\">Gen. 6:11-13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116903\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116903)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116903)\">Moses 7:36-37<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111092\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111092)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111092)\">2 Ne. 2:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111998\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111998)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111998)\">Alma 18:36<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112815\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112815)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112815)\">Morm. 9:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109381\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109381)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109381)\">Rom. 14:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116132\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116132)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116132)\">D&amp;C 128:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114838\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114838)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114838)\">D&amp;C 88:38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111076\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111076)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111076)\">2 Ne. 1:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111764\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111764)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111764)\">Alma 3:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111185\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111185)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111185)\">2 Ne. 9:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113284\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113284)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113284)\">D&amp;C 19:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107975\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107975)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107975)\">Matt. 12:32<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113734\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113734)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113734)\">D&amp;C 42:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114124\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114124)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114124)\">D&amp;C 59:23<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114884\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114884)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114884)\">D&amp;C 88:85<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115061\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115061)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115061)\">D&amp;C 93:52<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116840\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116840)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116840)\">Moses 6:59<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}